title: Beautiful floorplans to fit every budget. Stop by today!
posting_body: ['The Enclave', '10900 Bluffside Dr', 'Studio City, CA 91604', 'A wonderful home in Studio City is waiting for you!', 'We currently have a gorgeous 1 bedroom 1 bathroom renting for $2285 - $2325 per month.', 'This unit comes with 668 sq ft.', 'The Enclave Apartment community neighborhood is thoughtfully laid out for easy walking and biking, which makes a quick trip to the store or park no hassle at all.', 'Close proximity to the 110, 170, and 134 freeways means commuting to and from Studio City is a breeze, too, and takes some of the stress out of more extensive travel plans.', 'Also nearby, the Universal City Metro Orange Line can connect you to Downtown Los Angeles, Hollywood, and Warner Center within just a few minutes.', 'show contact info', 'Community Highlights:', '● Beautiful Courtyard', '● Elevator Service', '● Fitness Center', '● Laundry Facility', '● Soothing Spa', '● Sun Deck Area', '● Assigned Gated Subterranean Parking', '● Controlled Access Entry', '● Friendly, Professional On-Site Management', '● Responsive Maintenance', '● Social Area w/ BBQ Grills', 'Unit Highlights:', '● Air Conditioning', '● Balconies in Select Homes', '● Cable TV Ready', '● Dishwasher in Select Homes', '● Fireplace in Select Homes', '● Garbage Disposal', '● New Carpet in Select Homes', '● Refrigerator Available to Rent', '● Storage Space', '● Vertical Blinds', 'Contact:', 'show contact info', 'Website:', '<URL>/', 'Leasing Options:', '12-Month', 'Pet Policy:', 'Service Animals Accepted.', 'Sorry, No Pets.', 'Management:', 'Carlo, Inc', 'EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY', 'F25DD42FA5D44F']
